The '''Death Star Library''', or '''Library and Archives''' as it was officially known, was a large [[Library/Legends|library]] on [[Deck 106]] in [[Sector N-One/Legends|Sector N-One]] of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|original]] [[Death Star/Legends|Death Star]]. Most information in the library was transferred to [[phononic lattice storage]]. The library's data channel was 557.9. The library was destroyed when the Death Star exploded during the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]].

It was run by [[Atour Riten]].

